The paper deals with scene text detection and recognition, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves the use of a neural network (cs.AI) and the design of a novel layer (cs.LG) for feature extraction. The paper also discusses the use of previous methods and their limitations (cs.CL) and compares the proposed method with state-of-the-art techniques (cs.IR).
